Willis Towers Watson PLC: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback
















willis towers watson plc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Financials
Industry: Insurance
Sub-Industry: Insurance Brokers
Willis Towers Watson Public Limited Company operates as an advisory, broking, and solutions company. The Company provides a range of insurance brokerage, reinsurance, and risk management consulting services. Willis Towers Watson serves customers worldwide.




